{
  "stem": "232.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "We went down from the sidewalk, and they passed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Sometimes they beat you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Sometimes they just shouted dirty Jew at you, and you put your head away.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And if they were trying to beat you, you ran away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "That's all you can do.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And my uncle was pretty good.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "He was a violin player.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "He wanted me to learn to play the violin.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "He was also a pretty good painter painting pictures, landscapes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And I think in our family, it's a little bit artistic.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] and my sister had a beautiful voice.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "She always was singing very nice, and my brother and I, we were always joking around.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact, when my mother's brother got married in 1975, my uncle wrote a sketch for my brother and me to present at the wedding.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And it was a pretty funny sketch, because we spoke in Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "Usually German boys don't speak Yiddish, but we learned it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And it was a very nice success.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And I'll state where my brother always had a very, very nice voice.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And I never went in deeper to singing except of the choir in the temple, so we left it there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "In 1937, I started to learn for my bar mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "In Germany at that time, you needed at least a year to prepare for a bar mitzvah, because it is all in Hebrew, and it takes time to learn the songs, and the words, and everything.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And I started to learn.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "Well, to come back to 1936, when the Olympic games were played in Germany, all of a sudden, from all the benches, from all the parks the signs disappeared, because there were a lot of people from all over the world coming to Berlin.",
      "word_count": 44
    }
  ],
